commits.sourceNew:
@Test
  public void testSimpleChildDocs() throws Exception {
    String str = "{\n" +
        "    \"add\": {\n" +
        "        \"doc\": {\n" +
        "            \"id\": \"1\",\n" +
        "            \"_childDocuments_\": [\n" +
        "                {\n" +
        "                    \"id\": \"2\"\n" +
        "                },\n" +
        "                {\n" +
        "                    \"id\": \"3\",\n" +
        "                    \"foo_i\": [666,777]\n" +
        "                }\n" +
        "            ]\n" +
        "        }\n" +
        "    }\n" +
        "}";
    checkTwoChildDocs(str);
  }
